<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Rozszerzenia on Polskie filtry do AdBlocka, uBlocka Origin i AdGuarda</title><link>https://majkiit.github.io/polish-ads-filter/tags/rozszerzenia/</link><description>Recent content in Rozszerzenia on Polskie filtry do AdBlocka, uBlocka Origin i AdGuarda</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>pl</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 20:44:20 +0100</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://majkiit.github.io/polish-ads-filter/tags/rozszerzenia/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Jak skutecznie blokować reklamy w przeglądarkach internetowych na Androidzie?</title><link>https://majkiit.github.io/polish-ads-filter/docs/advanced/android-browser-adblocker/</link><pubDate>Sun, 18 Nov 2018 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://majkiit.github.io/polish-ads-filter/docs/advanced/android-browser-adblocker/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="a-firefoxfirefox--uboublock-origin">A) &lt;img src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/browser-logos/74.1.0/firefox/firefox_24x24.png" alt="Firefox" title="Mozilla Firefox">Firefox + &lt;img src="https://majkiit.github.io/polish-ads-filter/polish-ads-filter/images/uBO_24.png" alt="uBO">uBlock Origin&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>Po zainstalowaniu &lt;a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=org.mozilla.firefox" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Firefoxa&lt;/a> wystarczy wykonać parę kroków:&lt;/p>
&lt;ol>
&lt;li>Dotknij &lt;code>3 kropki =&amp;gt; Dodatki =&amp;gt; uBlock Origin =&amp;gt; + =&amp;gt; Dodaj&lt;/code>.&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Wybierz filtry, jakie chcesz. A jeśli 2 polskie ci nie wystarczają, to wejdź na &lt;a href="https://majkiit.github.io/polish-ads-filter/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">majkiit.github.io/polish-ads-filter&lt;/a> i zasubskrybuj dodatkowe.&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Gotowe!&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;h2 id="b-kiwikiwi--lemurlemur--uboublock-origin">B) &lt;img src="https://majkiit.github.io/polish-ads-filter/polish-ads-filter/images/kiwi_24.png" alt="Kiwi" title="Kiwi Browser">Kiwi / &lt;img src="https://majkiit.github.io/polish-ads-filter/polish-ads-filter/images/lemur_24.png" alt="Lemur" title="Lemur Browser">Lemur + &lt;img src="https://majkiit.github.io/polish-ads-filter/polish-ads-filter/images/uBO_24.png" alt="uBO">uBlock Origin&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>Po zainstalowaniu &lt;a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.kiwibrowser.browser" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Kiwi Browser&lt;/a> lub &lt;a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.lemurbrowser.exts" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Lemur Browser&lt;/a> wystarczy wykonać parę kroków:&lt;/p>
&lt;ol>
&lt;li>Wejdź na &lt;a href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ublock-origin/cjpalhdlnbpafiamejdnhcphjbkeiagm" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ublock-origin/cjpalhdlnbpafiamejdnhcphjbkeiagm&lt;/a>, dotknij &lt;strong>dodaj do Chrome&lt;/strong>, a następnie potwierdź instalację.&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Wybierz filtry, jakie chcesz. A jeśli 2 polskie ci nie wystarczają, to wejdź na &lt;a href="https://majkiit.github.io/polish-ads-filter/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">majkiit.github.io/polish-ads-filter&lt;/a> i zasubskrybuj dodatkowe.&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Gotowe!&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;h2 id="c-edge-canarymicrosoft-edge-canary--uboublock-origin">C) &lt;img src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/browser-logos/74.1.0/edge-canary/edge-canary_24x24.png" alt="Edge Canary">Microsoft Edge Canary + &lt;img src="https://majkiit.github.io/polish-ads-filter/polish-ads-filter/images/uBO_24.png" alt="uBO">uBlock Origin&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>Po zainstalowaniu &lt;a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.microsoft.emmx.canary" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Edge Canary&lt;/a> wystarczy wykonać parę kroków:&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>